name: v1.8.1
body:
* Higher quality audio recordings
* Fixed bug where uploading would stop
* Fixed bug where manual uploading would stop if a recording was triggered with flight mode activated

name: test-v1.7.6
body: Added permissions check when viewing Rooted view in Advanced Options

name: beta-v1.6.1
body:
Fixes potentially recordings not triggering after update

Asks for superuser access when rooted is enabled

name: Bird Count with notes, Easy GPS update
body:
Bird count with notes: Allows you to record while doing a manual bird count.
GPS: Can now update the GPS location from the main screen.
Fix regression: Groups update from server.

name: Bird Count with notes. Update GPS from main screen.
body:
Added the ability to add extra notes for a bird count recording.  These notes are uploaded to the server as metadata.

Also added the ability to update the GPS location from the main screen.

name: 5 (10, 15) minute bird count
body:
Added 5 (10 and 15)  minute Bird Count feature.

Removed 'Walking mode' feature.

Fixed permissions issue for Android OS >= 6

name: v1.3.9
body: Fixes permission issue for devices running Android OS >= 6

name: v.1.3.7
body: Record Now button - records even when Recording has been disabled

name: v 1.3.5 Beta
body:
Added message to explain that you can swipe left/right.  Shortened the title of the first screen in Advanced to make it clearer that you can swipe.

Issue - Very Advanced - Audio Source setting screen does not fit. Fixed: I've put the radio buttons in a scroll view..
